{"tid":1363735,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我們是一眾熱愛香港的HKT員工","createTime":"2019-07-25T08:37:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T13:45:30.000Z","uid":1639,"like":81,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"8657f6442ee2b0fb3ebbe75d34605b9a69df6e5b","tid":1363735,"uid":1639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:37:22.000Z","msg":"致各位香港市民：<br />\n<br />\n我們是一班熱愛香港、來自HKT的員工。自政府強硬推出引渡條例以來，短短一個多月期間，香港已經發生連串示威集會。然而， <br />\n一眾以特首林鄭月娥為首的政府高官，一直寞視民意，只以「暫緩」、「壽終正寢」等模稜兩可的語言偽術，堅拒徹回條例。<br />\n<br />\n而由六月九日直至七月二十一日，由起初於政府總部所施放的催淚彈，直到在上環開出至少36發橡膠子彈，警方於多次示威衝突中 <br />\n使用不對等的武力驅散示威者，令多名示威者受傷流血。政府時已至今仍然拒絕正面回應、拒絕成立獨立調查委員會調查有關事件 <br />\n及涉事警員，繼續以官腔呼籲利用形同虛設的現有投訴機制處理事件，如此態度乃是不負責任，難以向廣大市民交代。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z2NAwNU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz2NAwNU.gif&h=b2861d3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而於七月二十一日，一群白衫人士於元朗西鐵站內無差別攻擊市民，事件導致45人受傷，其中一人危殆，傷者甚至包括一眾包括老人及孕婦的無辜市民。事發當天警方不單沒有立即到場調停及阻止事件，甚至有影片顯示有警員於現場轉身而去，999熱線無法接通，警署拉閘拒絕市民報案，於白衫人士散去後方派員到場。影片更顯示警方以及立法會議員何君堯與一眾白衫人士談笑風生，何君堯更稱白衫人士為「英雄」。警黑勾結早已證據確鑿，政府及何君堯一直顛倒是非黑白，還是社會早已道德淪喪，施暴者方為「英雄」？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9o78RN3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9o78RN3.png&h=56cba7f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qJe3FGD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqJe3FGD.png&h=5d68fa43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我們並非公務員，但仍會一直謹守崗位、以專業的態度服務香港市民。社會撕裂、政府管治無能已是不爭的事實，我們懇請政府盡快政面回應市民訴求，全面徹查事件，讓市民無需再生活於恐懼的陰霾下，讓香港早日重回正軌。<br />\n<br />\n一眾熱愛香港的HKT員工上<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C919Be5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC919Be5.png&h=082ac8b6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f4421cbac97ea7857fd8c138dcde7fc96d865f0b","tid":1363735,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:39:41.000Z","msg":"推 支持"},{"pid":"d0f47b45b1c5635a395335ee4d0a123b5dec4be8","tid":1363735,"uid":47783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:39:45.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"acb40768b80b100283fe658f25d7f3ba07eae06b","tid":1363735,"uid":46433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:40:20.000Z","msg":"gchi！"},{"pid":"ed311775f00ca7c18eff2bb8f16d954fcdfa7f23","tid":1363735,"uid":279085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:41:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zfNKZRPQHZk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzfNKZRPQHZk&d=9aIS%2Fhk2hxf5w8hb7WAMUa7XYz%2BrpCtmef%2B4BlhZTRs%3D&h=8b14d93e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zfNKZRPQHZk</a>"},{"pid":"eecb938c248492fc4a6e33cc03ad28b8455d4895","tid":1363735,"uid":260488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:41:34.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"dacb92ee42d3403fc4f4d2d27f7ad1116bfa35da","tid":1363735,"uid":146187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:41:49.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b0cfc4017aa3504581eaa1cf68612a32f7b47fac","tid":1363735,"uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:42:52.000Z","msg":"我冇野講<br />\n我要見律師"},{"pid":"e547699d71a8a94aa7692634c2583fa91f877093","tid":1363735,"uid":242116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:43:01.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n支持！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0ea191adc5966c82330fc4135bdae0993eaae20","tid":1363735,"uid":115714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:47:29.000Z","msg":"小埋表示支持"},{"pid":"e5e85071a789e86320b8075b720c74d8b59fab3a","tid":1363735,"uid":217376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:48:24.000Z","msg":"多謝你哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class